{"tid":294590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宣揚國威？傳「遼寧艦」下月訪港 慶祝香港回歸中國20周年","createTime":"2017-06-23T05:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T12:27:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"510bd2532330adad5105ee6734ec089964633008","tid":294590,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"宣揚國威？「遼寧艦」下月訪港 慶祝香港回歸中國20周年<br />\n<br />\n中央社&nbsp;2017年06月23日 10:30 風傳媒<br />\n<br />\n香港媒體報導，中國第一艘航空母艦遼寧艦預定下月訪問香港，以慶祝香港主權轉移20週年。據了解，這項訪問計畫是由中國國家主席、中央軍事委員會主席習近平親自拍板。<br />\n<br />\n星島日報今天報導，遼寧艦下月訪港期間，將首度開放給香港市民參觀。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述消息人士說，尚不清楚遼寧艦訪港的具體日期，但應會在北京中央領導人訪港之後，由大陸海軍高層將領率同來訪。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，遼寧艦訪港是由習近平親自拍板的，希望讓港人了解大陸海軍的實力和發展，增強民族自豪感。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.storm.mg/article/287703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F287703&d=bPPmmc9j%2BMC%2BUdakK3fAxS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c9734ddd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.storm.mg/article/287703</a>"},{"pid":"675f764572c095800a6b325a64d394219c3e40bc","tid":294590,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"懾服港獨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb0e8b52a72068737bcb926f18f80d4b98278ef","tid":294590,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"渣隻垃圾過黎真係增強哂支那人既柒感"},{"pid":"222cbc184c60f82cbaace9e1c653d11457fd1aa2","tid":294590,"uid":5542,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:00:07.000Z","msg":"污染空氣"},{"pid":"4e7918ee71f98e014b507d0b0e69474951ffc74f","tid":294590,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣隻垃圾過黎真係增強哂支那人既柒感</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s